      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ZIPPING MONROE (7) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a 0.8 lengths second (18.39) behind Isabella Kade at this track. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Expected to feature in the finish again. LITTLE ESMERALDA (6) pinged the lids from out wide but run ended and faded out of it late when 5th at this track in Grade 5 company. Better than last start and can bounce back. HELLO NEMO (2) was out of character last run when missing the frame, finishing eighth (19.25) in a Grade 5 at this track. Normally safely away but always well back and facing a task from wide out last time. Form here at this distance is sound. Can do much better this time. BARSTOOL DOLLARS (1) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
